Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Sincro: wyxchari
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,基于 opentitles.org 英文字幕翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(注意：本字幕针对2020年动画版视频,\N与旧版本在对话内容和时间轴上略有差异)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,【中文翻译/时间轴】巴蛮子sz
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\b1}The Faceless Ones: Episode 5{\b\b}\N{\b1\b1}无面一族: 第五集{\b\b}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,海上救援队报告说没有找到, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Negative report from Air Sea Rescue, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但有两架飞机掉了, 肯定会有残骸的痕迹啊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But with two aircraft ditching,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}there must be some signs of wreckage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么觉得变色龙的飞机是坠落到海里了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Why do you think the Chameleon plane\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}crashed into the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它从我们的雷达屏幕上消失了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Because it disappeared off our radar screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但它一开始是静止没动!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But it stood still first!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它肯定是跟空军的飞机撞上了, 然后掉落下去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Because it must have collided with\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the RAF plane and dropped like a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么会这么想\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道, 当一架飞机像那样在雷达上静止不动\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You see, when a plane on that radar\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}appears to stand still,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那么它事实上就是直线下落了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}it is in point of fact dropping straight down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 直线上升怎么样?   - 噢, 我亲爱的博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What about straight up? - Oh my dear Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要能像那样跑出我们雷达的范围\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}To get above our radar umbrella like that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,它必须垂直爬上达到100英里高\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}it would have to climb vertically\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}until it was a hundred miles high.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那该死的高度就是外太空了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The darned thing would be in outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,正是这个!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那架派来跟踪我们的飞机, 咱们要摧毁它吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That plane they sent to follow us.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Should we have destroyed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.11,0:01:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的玩具飞机, 我们可以消灭他们一个中队\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We could eliminate a whole squadron of their toy planes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而他们一点都够不着我们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and they'd never get on to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的脑子应付不了这样的行动\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Their minds can't cope with an operation like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要记得我们总管的教导：地球人的智力...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Remember the teaching of our Director -\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the intelligence of Earth people...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:02:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...只跟我们星球的动物差不多\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}...is comparable only to that of animals on our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说我漏掉了一个, 还在想你出了什么状况\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I thought I'd missed one of you.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I wondered what happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你对他们做什么了?   - 关上抽屉\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What have you done to them?!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Close that drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不... 不...不要. 别碰我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No... No... Don't. leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 谢谢你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,海上救援队说他们还在搜索, 但仍然没有任何痕迹\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Air Sea Rescue say they're still searching\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but there's no trace yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Commandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了. 飞行员成功逃生了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I see - did the pilot managed to bail out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我很遗憾\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们发现了空军飞机的残骸\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They've found the remains of that RAF plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行员已经被电死了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The pilot had been electrocuted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你还觉得这些人是来自地球?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you still think these people are from Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道, 博士. 我不知道该怎么思考了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't know, Doctor.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I just don't know what to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但凡有那么一丝确凿的证据就好了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}If only there was one solid piece of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得证据正好进来了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think it's just come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你介意我去盘问他吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you mind if I question him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我知道怎么撬开他的嘴\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think I know how to make him talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这是什么东西, 对吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You know what this is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,噢, 我觉得你知道. 把你的袖子卷起来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh I think you do.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Roll up your sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须得听他的吗, 先生?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do I have to take orders from him, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该解释一下, 博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think perhaps you should explain, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟, 这个人是为我工作的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}After all, this man is working for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,只是你觉得他在为你工作!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You only think he's working for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,总指挥, 你的人员正在被系统性地替换掉\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Commandant, your personnel\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}are being systematically replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而这就是他们替换的方法\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And this is how they're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这人不是 Meadows, 只是看起来像 Meadows\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is not Meadows, it only looks like Meadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而他的一个胳膊上带着一个这样的东西\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He's wearing one of these things on his arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧, 按他说的做\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Very well, do as he asks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是先生, 这太荒谬了 - 我们都得为这事出力\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- But sir, this is ridiculous...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- We all have to help in this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Meadows, 卷起你的袖子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Meadows. Roll up your sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,拦住他!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}STOP HIM!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把他弄到椅子上\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now get him in this chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean, 叫警察\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jean, send for the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 博士, 继续\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right Doctor, go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,卷起他的左袖\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Roll up his left sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了, 现在开始\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There we are. Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我转动这里面一个旋钮, 会怎样?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What happens if I were to turn one of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰它!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, 我明白了. 好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah, I see. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那么现在, 你得回答我所有的问题了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now then, you are going to answer all my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而作为回报, 我承诺不会伤害你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And in return, I promise no harm will come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你明白了吗?   - 好吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Do you understand?   - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的飞机把所有的乘客带到哪里去了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Where are your planes taking all their passengers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有一颗卫星, 大约在150英里高空\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There's a satellite,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}about a hundred and fifty miles up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们为什么要绑架这些年轻人》\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Why are you abducting all these young people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的星球发生了一场大灾难, 一次巨大的爆炸\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We had a catastrophe on our planet.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A gigantic explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所见, 我们已经失去了自己的身份\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}As you've seen, we have lost our identities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的人要灭亡了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}My people are dying out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们的人对你们有什么用?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But what use would our people be to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的科学家研究出来一个方法\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Our scientists devised a process...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可以让我们得到另外一种生物的物理形体\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}so that we could take on the\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}physical characterises of another being.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,而这就是这种方法的其中一步?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is part of the process?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 这就是为什么你不能碰那个\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, that's why you mustn't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们打算绑架多少年轻人?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}How many of these young people\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}do you hope to abduct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这一次 - 四万  - 四万!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- This time, fifty thousand.  - Fifty thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这个卫星有多大?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}How large is this satellite?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们的飞机上, 这些乘客会被缩小\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}On the journey in our planes,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the passengers are miniaturised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了. 你们有多少人在盖特威克机场?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I see. How many of your people\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}are working here at Gatwick Airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是真的, 我跟你说, 我不知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That's the truth, I tell you. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧. 那我们的人怎么样了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Very well. What happens to the people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们那些被换到身份的人, 那些原身?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}whose identities have been taken over, the originals?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在机场某个地方, 我...我不知道具体在哪里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They're somewhere in the Airport,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I... I don't know exactly where.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我把这个地方翻个底朝天, 也要找到他们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll have the whole place\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}torn to pieces to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不, 你不能去找他们  - 为什么不能?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- No, you mustn't find them. -  Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们...不能去, 就是不能去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You... you mustn't, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果我们真找到他们, 就会在他们胳膊上找到这个, 嗯?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Because if we do find them\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}we'll find one of these on their arms, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而如果我们卸下它, 就会有可怕的事情发生在你们身上?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And if we remove it,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}something terrible will happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们必须换回来怎么办?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What if you have to change back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 那可以实现, 但需要机器\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, that can be done, but with the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 医护中心的那个机器?   - 对\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- The machine in the Medical Centre?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们谁也不知道我们的原身在哪里, 只有那个护士知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}None of us know where our own originals are.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Except that Nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,护士? 她什么情况?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Nurse? What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她比较精明, 把她的原身带在身边的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh she was cunning.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}She's got her own original with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在哪里?   - 我不知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Where is it?  - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think you do know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在, 你打算告诉我不?   - 在医护中心\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Now, are you going to tell me?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- It's in the Medical Centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很好, 你得只给我看具体是哪里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right. You're going to show me where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我不敢, 她会摧毁我的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I... I daren't. She'll have me destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你是打算合作呢, 还是不合作?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you going to co-operate or are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧, 反正也没什么区别了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right. It won't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你再也见不到那五万个年轻人了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You'll never see those\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}fifty thousand young people again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我最好把他带过去 - 医护中心\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think I'd better take him down\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}there - the Medical Centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩. 我们怎么处置她?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This girl. What do we do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要把她用作原身\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We need to use her as an original.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们就可以安排一个我们的人...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That way we can get one of our people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...在那个威胁我们的家伙身边\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}...close to the man who is menacing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就可以杀了他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He will then be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但 Blade 机长没打算再带我们的人去地球...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But surely Captain Blade isn't\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}bringing any more of our people to Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,带他进来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕我没搞懂\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm afraid I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你们俩有些共同点\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think you two have something in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人病了吗, 警官?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Is this man ill, officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,卷起你的袖子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Roll up your sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在说些什么?   - 警官!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What are you talking about?   - Officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,请把你的手拿开\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Please take your hands off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题. 我想看的都看到了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Certainly. I've seen all I want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我来拿着这个, 如果你不介意的话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll have that, if you don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 她的真身在哪里?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now then, where is her original?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里面\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不能进里面去!   - 你还是愿意被毁灭吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You can't go in there!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Would you rather be destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看着他, 警官\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Keep an eye on her, officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,把他带过来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Bring him along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam! Sam, 你没事吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Sam! Sam, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吧, Sam!   - 还好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Are you all right Sam!  - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为我完蛋了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I thought I was done for there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 手脚发麻  - 你运气好没有变得更严重\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Pins and needles...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You're lucky it was no worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你这是要干什么?   - 只是检查一下\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What are you doing? - Just checking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 护士的原身在哪里?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now then, where is the Nurse's original?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在墙里某处的嵌板里面\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's in a panel in the wall somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,开关在躺椅里面\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The control's in the couch there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 警官\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼诶, 她还真在里面\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Flipping heck! But she's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你个叛徒!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小心!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了 Sam, 没事了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's all right Sam. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她消失了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}She's vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,把她放到那儿\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Put her on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就这里吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 会造成永久性损伤吗?   - 不会\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Will there be any permanent damage?  - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把那个拿下来了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You can take that off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了, 再过一两分钟你就完全没事了, 来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's all right. You'll be quite all right\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}in a few minutes. There.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,博士, Jamie 他怎么了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor, what's happened to Jamie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这些东西到底是做什么用的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What on Earth are these doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,博士, Jamie上一次并不在柜台附近\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor, Jamie wasn't anywhere\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}near the kiosk the last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿你根本没在听, 我觉得他们抓走了Jamie!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look you're not listening.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think they've got Jamie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jamie! 哪儿?   - 你应该知道的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Jamie! Where?!  - Well you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你让他顺走了我的机票?  - 顺走你的机票?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You got him to pinch me ticket!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Pinch your ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为了阻止我去罗马\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}To stop me from going to Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢, 你是说 Jamie  - 顶替了我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh you mean Jamie...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Has gone in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,先是 Polly 和 Ben, 现在又是 Jamie\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}First Polly and Ben, and now Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能再耽误时间了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We've no time to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,督察!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看看我能不能把你弄出来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Let's see if I can get you out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么到这里来的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我...坐飞机来的, 偷了别人的票\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I... I came on the plane, stole someone's ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该在路上就被小型化了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You ought to have been miniaturised on the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小... 小型化?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Min... miniaturised?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,被缩小了, 就像柜子里所有这些年轻人这样\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Reduced in size - like all the\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}youngsters in these cabins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有吃喝什么吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Did you not have anything to eat or drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没有, 我...觉得太难受了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, I... I felt too ill!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这就能解释了, 那些食物是整个过程中的第一步\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That explains it. The food is\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the first part of the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,督察, 这是什么地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Inspector, what is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:13:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一颗卫星, Jamie. 在太空的一艘飞船\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A satellite, Jamie. A flying ship in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人来自另外的星球, 看起来博士一直都是对的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}These people are from another planet.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It seems the Doctor was right after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在下面有人相信他吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Does anyone down there believe him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,噢, 我...不太清楚. 我...估计没有\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh I... I'm not sure. I... I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我估计这对他们来说太难以置信了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I suppose it is too much for them to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但博士肯定已经让他们相信有事发生了吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But surely the Doctor's convinced them\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}that something is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯, 我觉得总指挥可能...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Aye, I think maybe the Commandant...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, Jamie\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,督察, 你是逃出来的还是怎么的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Inspector, have you escaped or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没谁能从这里逃走\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No-one escapes from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那架飞到这里的飞机...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But the plane that comes here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它肯定会回到地球去, 我们可以登上它\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}... it must go back to Earth.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We could get on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一趟飞往地球的飞机正在离开\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The last plane to Earth is leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是回去接他们自己的人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They've just gone back to pick up their own people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定博士会想到什么方法救我们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Surely the Doctor will think of some way of rescuing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这次不行了, Jamie\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Not this time, Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次, 他要对付的是比他还高级的脑子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This time, he's up against\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}a mind superior even to his.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,总管的脑子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The mind of the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说比博士还聪明?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You mean someone clever than the Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是负责这整个行动的人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The man in charge of this whole mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你似乎知道得不少, 督察\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You seem to know a lot about it, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然知道, Jamie. 我就是总管!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Of course I do, Jamie. I am the Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙飞机就是在这个方位消失的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is the bearing\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}where the Chameleon plane vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道它会不会重新在这里出现\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I want to know if it reappears there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们下一个航班快到时间了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They've a flight due any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很好先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Very good sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,博士, 这些人事档案是怎么回事?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now then Doctor, what's\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}all this about personnel files?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,过来, 我展示给你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Over here, I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我在医疗中心找到这些的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I found these in the Medical Centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,记录属于25个在这里工作的人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Records of twenty-five people who work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,每一个都被变色龙给替换掉了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Each one of these has been taken over by Chameleons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 我会安排人在15分钟内将他们都抓起来!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right. I'll have them all\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}under arrest within fifteen minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Airport Police please.\N请接机场警局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在看看这个  - 这是什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Now look at this.   - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙的飞行排班表\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Chameleon Air Schedules.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了没? 他们这个季节的最后一班还有不到一个小时\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You see here? Their last flight\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of the season goes in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,呃..请接 Reynolds 警司\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Er.. Superintendent Reynolds please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一班? 那他们就不能抓了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The last flight? Well that's exactly\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}why they mustn't be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,警司吗? 我是总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Superintendent? Commandant here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能听我说吗!   - 你能等一会儿吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Will you please listen to me!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Will you hold on a moment please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这些人不能抓  - 为什么不能?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- These people must not be arrested. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在外太空某个地方...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Somewhere in outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还有五万个年轻人, 包括我的三个朋友\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}there are fifty thousand young people,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}three of my friends amongst them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得想办法把他们弄回来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and somehow we've got to bring them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想登上这趟最后的航班\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I want to get on this last flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也就意味着得让变色龙认为一切正常\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}which means the Chameleons must think that\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}everything is going according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,总指挥?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Commandant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Reynolds, 我回头再打给你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Reynolds, I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在怎样?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,光点. 突然凭空出现了, 正朝这边过来!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This blip. It's just appeared out of nowhere\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and it's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 跟踪住他们. 可能是变色龙的飞机回来了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right well keep tracking them.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It may be the Chameleon plane returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,现在看这里, 博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now look here, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都在说登上那架飞机, 但怎么做到?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All very well talking about\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}getting on that plane, but how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,当前来看, 你看起来像是一个叫 Meadows 的人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}At the moment, you look like a man called Meadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你能移除这个身份, 变成另外一个人吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Could you shed that identity\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and become somebody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可以, 我们中有些人被处理过两次\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes. Yes, some of our people\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}have been processed twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好. 那这样的话我就假装成一个变色龙, 就这样上去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Good. Then in that case I shall pretend\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I am a Chameleon, and get on board that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你登上那架飞机, 你期望能做些什么呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But even if you get on that plane,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}what do you hope to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道, 得等到了卫星之后再说\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't know until I get to the satellite...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而我只有一张牌可以打\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and then I will have one card to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 而这就取决于你了, 总指挥  - 什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- And that's up to you Commandant. - What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那些被变色龙顶替掉的人, 那些真身\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The people the Chameleons\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}have taken over, the originals,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,被藏在盖特威克机场某个地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}are hidden somewhere here in Gatwick Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你必须给找出来  - 当然\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You have got to find them.  - Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还得把那恐怖的东西从他们胳膊上卸下来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and get those fearful things off their arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不, 不, 不! 用尽各种方法, 找到他们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, no, no! Find them, by all means,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但不要去动胳膊上的护套\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but don't tamper with those arm sheaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我们就失去了威胁手段\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Otherwise we lose our one threat -
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,而这可能是我同他们讨价还价的唯一筹码!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the one thing I may be able to bargain with!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了. 但我还是没明白你怎么能登上飞机\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes I see that. But I still don't see\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}how you're going to get on that plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,更别说让他们相信, 你是他们一员\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}let alone convince them\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}that you're one of their people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那就得完全有赖于 Pinto 护士了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That will depend entirely on Nurse Pinto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean, 接警司 Reynolds\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jean, get onto Superintendent. Reynolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,现在一切都清楚了吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now is everything clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定你理解了我要让你做什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're sure you understand\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}what I am asking you to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,当然, 但我们得为那些年轻人考虑\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, of course, but we've got to\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}think of those young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是省事啊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}How very convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 锁上门  - 别, 别开枪!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Lock the door.  - No, don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是 Meadows, 他已经被重新转化了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is Meadows. He had to be re-processed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,博士已经很怀疑我的那个 Meadows 身份了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Doctor became too suspicious of me as Meadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我成功绑架了他, 然后就是你眼前这个人了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I was able to kidnap him.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The rest is as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有点遗憾, 本来有个人在航空控制塔台会很有用的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A pity. It was useful having\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}someone in Air Traffic Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当然我们掌控住了博士的脑子也很不错\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But then of course we have possession\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of the Doctor's brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得它会很有用吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You think that will be useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Undoubtedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说你会带我们到卫星上去?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That means that you'll be taking us\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}up to the satellite?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,下一班我会带上所有人回到卫星\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I am taking everybody back to\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the satellite on the next plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后一班了, 这你肯定没忘吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's the last flight.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Surely you haven't forgotten that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,二次处理, 太难记清楚细节了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The re-processing.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's difficult to remember details.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 当然, 我理解\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, of course, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他的原身怎么样了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What have you done with his original?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在一个安全的地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}In a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,跟其它的在一起\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It should be with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉具体是哪儿, 我安排转过来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Tell me where that is\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and I'll have it transferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间干这个了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There's no time for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenkins 会帮你搞定出入境手续的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jenkins will see you through Immigration.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会在15分钟后离开\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We leave in fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得我们骗过他了吗?   - 说不好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Do you think we convinced him?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说我们可以上那架飞机了, 快, 我们别晚了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}However we've got aboard that plane.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Come on, don't let's be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好的, 谢谢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是警方打来的, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That was the police, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说变色龙飞机的乘客已经在登机了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They say the passengers are now\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}boarding the Chameleon plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看到博士登上飞机了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Did they see if the Doctor had got on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了, 他和 Pinto 护士一起\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes. He was with Nurse Pinto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所有乘客都是成年人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All the passengers are adults
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们中的大多数人都是机场职员\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and most of them have been\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}identified as airport personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,总指挥, 变色龙飞机请求起飞\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Commandant. Chameleon plane's requesting\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}clearance for start up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 Heslington, 程序照常, 给他们许可\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right Heslington, normal procedure.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Give them clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙345, 请准备\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Chameleon Three-Four-Five,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}stand by for start temperature...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是了, 现在又是静止状态了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes. Now it's stationary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,它肯定又在垂直爬升\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It must be ascending vertically.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,光点变弱了, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The blip's getting fainter, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是说他已经超出了我们雷达的范围\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That means he's rising above our radar umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, 警司, 终于找到你了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah Superintendent, the very man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,光点消失了, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Blip's just gone, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你看, Reynolds\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now look, Reynolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得把你那里的每一个人都派去搜寻\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We've got to get every man\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of your force on that search.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一刻也不能浪费. 我们的时间不多了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There isn't a moment to lose.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Time's running out on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有收获吗?   - 没, 看那个!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Any luck?  - No. Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,期望我的文件跟这一样整齐!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Wish my files were as neat as that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么样, 柜台那里有什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}How about you. What about the kiosk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么, 只有一些文件\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Not much. Just a few papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,唔, 我们最好回到塔台去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hmm... Oh we'd better get back\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to Air Traffic Control then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎样?   - 就有一些文件, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Well?  - Just a few papers sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,也好, 也许里面有点线索\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, there might be a clue there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,总指挥, 他们肯定是把他们放到某个地方了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Commandant, surely they'd\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}put them somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是, 某个我们不会想到的地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I mean, well somewhere we'd never think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得好好想想, Jean, 不管它是哪儿\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We've got to think of it, Jean, wherever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,博士还指望我们呢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Doctor's relying on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:20:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,成千上万人的性命有赖于我们找到那些原身, 还得快!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Thousands of lives are depending on us\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}finding those originals - and quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还有多久, 博士?   - 我不知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- How much longer, Doctor?  - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们快到了, 别担心\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I should think we're almost there. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}One moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,由于我们的行动取得了圆满成功\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Owing to the complete success of our operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的卫星上的生存空间不得不用来存放...货物\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}living space on our satellite\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}has had to be used for our... cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以, 舱室会重新分配\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Therefore, quarters will be re-allocated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,向住宿中心报告以获得指示\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Report to the accommodation centre\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}for instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他起疑心了没?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you think he's suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,说不好, 我们先跟其他人走吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't know. Let's follow the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,重试一遍, 你叫什么名字?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Try again, What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jami​e\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪里来?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Where do you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,从地球, 一个叫做苏格兰的地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}From Earth, a place called Scotland.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 总管  - 什么事?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Director.  - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发现了两个冒牌货：博士和 Pinto 护士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We have found two impostors.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Doctor and Nurse Pinto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我请求授权我去消灭他们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I want permission to have them destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下, 对于博士你都知道些什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}One moment. What do you know about the Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是这个星球也不是这个时代的人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He is not of this Earth or of this century.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他穿越过时空\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He has travelled through time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他的知识甚至超过我们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}His knowledge is even greater than ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,总管, 这个人对我们是个危险, 必须被消灭\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Director, this man is a danger to us,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}he should be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但我说他必须活着 - 不过是作为我们的一员\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And I say he must live - but as one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你会后悔的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You will regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你收到命令了, Blade 机长\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You have your orders, Captain Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在怎么办?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开溜, 看看我们能后找到那些年轻人, 快点\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We slip away and see if we can\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}find these young people. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, Blade 机长, 我们正在按你的指令...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah, Captain Blade,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}we're carrying out your instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...在找住宿中心\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We're looking for the accommodation centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我的指令对你们不适用\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}My instructions don't apply to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩将不再需要居住空间了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You two won't be needing living space.
